      "content": "Wait, what? Goblins? I'm not sure what you mean by that. I'm just looking for actual flight advice. Can we just stick to the logistics? Between Doha and Dubai, which one usually has faster connection times for a flight heading to Singapore? I don't have much time to browse everything.",
